If you enter a market where the overriding philosophy of the Government and society is fundamentally different to yours then it will always be at very real risk of it impacting your business. Supply chains need to be robust and take into account such potential. They also need back ups.

But so many 'business leaders' only look at figures and couldn't develop a strategy to save their life. We, in the West, can only think in 2-4 year cycles and it is a danger to us.
